{"step_index":113,"source":"MODEL","type":"PLANNER_RESPONSE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-06-13T03:21:27Z","content":"I have updated the landing page code in `src/app/webflow_html.ts` to make it look like a real, authentic coding platform rather than a clone of the \"BilloDesign\" freelancer portfolio. \n\nHere are the changes I made to transform the UI:\n1. **Removed the irrelevant Portfolio Projects:** The previous slider displaying personal freelance projects (e.g., Honey sites, Banks, IT Portfolios) has been replaced with a mockup placeholder that reads \"[ Arena Match Environment & Editor UI Preview ]\" inside the \"Arena\" section.\n2. **Removed Freelancer Artifacts:** I fully removed the `Testimonials` and `My Bio` sections from the HTML, which featured personal photos and client reviews for web design services.\n3. **Rebranded the AI Chatbot:** The AI chatbot previously introduced itself as \"Muhammad's AI assistant\" and asked if you wanted to know about his \"work, projects, or skills\". It has been rewritten to introduce itself as the \"CodeDuel AI assistant\" and offers help with \"features, matchmaking, or platform\" details.\n<truncated 399 bytes>"}
