{"step_index":232,"source":"MODEL","type":"PLANNER_RESPONSE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-06-13T03:36:01Z","content":"I have completely overhauled the design of the landing page to remove the \"BilloDesign\" template feel and give it a premium, authentic CodeDuel identity!\n\nHere are the specific design changes I implemented:\n\n1. **Awwwards Ribbon Removed:** I completely removed the floating \"W.\" Awwwards Nominee ribbon from the UI so it doesn't look like a template.\n2. **\"Scroll Down\" Text Replaced:** I removed the generic \"Scroll down and I'll guide you\" from the typing animation and replaced it with a much more fitting \"Enter the arena.\" and \"Compete. Code. Conquer.\"\n3. **Custom SVG Logo:** I replaced the generic text logo with a cool, glowing SVG icon (with no background, just as you requested) to make it look like a genuine, branded product.\n4. **Glassmorphism & New Background:** Pure black is gone! I implemented a sleek `radial-gradient` background blending deep neon purple (`#2a0a4a`) into a dark canvas (`#050505`). It gives the whole page a modern glassmorphic and professional vibe.\n<truncated 521 bytes>"}
