{"step_index":628,"source":"MODEL","type":"PLANNER_RESPONSE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-06-13T05:06:02Z","content":"I have completely ripped out the bloated Webflow injection and **refactored the entire landing page from scratch into an ultra-lightweight (\"feather style\"), highly optimized native Next.js + Tailwind React component.**\n\n### Here is what I did to achieve maximum performance and visual fidelity:\n1. **Deleted the massive `webflow_html.ts` file.** (It was over 1600+ lines of raw HTML strings that were slowing down Next.js hydration).\n2. **Built a Pure React/Tailwind Landing Page (`src/app/page.tsx`):**\n   * **Glowing Background Orbs:** Instead of loading heavy scripts, I created stunning atmospheric background orbs using pure CSS (`blur-[150px]`, `animate-pulse`) for absolute zero JS overhead.\n   * **Hero Section:** Added massive \"CODE BEYOND LIMITS.\" typography with a beautiful transparent text gradient and drop shadows.\n   * **Glassmorphic Floating Stats:** Built three floating stat cards (Active Players, Matches Played, Avg Wait Time) using Tailwind's `backdrop-blur-xl` and `bg-white/5` utilities.\n<truncated 556 bytes>"}
